Company Overview of Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading, financial services, and information technology businesses in Hong Kong and Mainland China. Its Trading Business segment trades in goods, components, and accessories. It trades in various brands of milk powder products to customers based in Hong Kong; and beauty products, confectioneries, and pharmacy products. The company’s Financial Services Business segment provides financial leasing, money lending, and securities brokerage services; and operates as a book-runner, as well as a lead manager in respect of issuance of debts listed in Europe. Its Information Technology Business segment engages in the d...
Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading, financial services, and information technology businesses in Hong Kong and Mainland China. Its Trading Business segment trades in goods, components, and accessories. It trades in various brands of milk powder products to customers based in Hong Kong; and beauty products, confectioneries, and pharmacy products. The company’s Financial Services Business segment provides financial leasing, money lending, and securities brokerage services; and operates as a book-runner, as well as a lead manager in respect of issuance of debts listed in Europe. Its Information Technology Business segment engages in the distributorship of information technology products, and provision of relevant technical support services; and developing mobile and cloud based application software, and operating related e-commence platform. The company’s Other Business segment engages in servicing business, such as training course provision. The company was formerly known as Merdeka Mobile Group Limited and changed its name to Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited in October 2015. Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Merdeka Financial Services Group Limited is a subsidiary of Ivana Investments Limited.
